OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers only
OL,6,Fslowly easing overnight, however most
OL,7,Fareas should become largely dry by
OL,8,Fdawn. A brisk breeze continuing
OL,9,Fovernight, with temperatures on the
OL,10,Fmild side.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FVariable cloud with
OL,13,Fscattered showers and some bright
OL,14,Fspells, Patchy rain may affect the
OL,15,FPeak District at times. A brisk breeze
OL,16,Fbut feeling warmer.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
