OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FThursday, patchy rain easing north
OL,7,Fthen dry and warmer. Friday, very warm
OL,8,Fsunny spells. Chance of thundery
OL,9,Fevening showers. Saturday, very warm
OL,10,Fwith bright spells, thundery showers
OL,11,Fstill possible.
